dogecoin.text:
@elonmusk “Dear Elon Mask
I trusted you and invested in Dogecoin with the hope of a brighter future. Unfortunately, instead of rising, it fell even further. I understand that these things can be unpredictable, but please help support the loyal community that believes in Dogecoin.

@elonmusk @Rep_Stansbury “Dear Elon Mask
I trusted you and invested in Dogecoin with the hope of a brighter future. Unfortunately, instead of rising, it fell even further. I understand that these things can be unpredictable, but please help support the loyal community that believes in Dogecoin.

@elonmusk We’re not asking for much—just enough to make a difference in our lives. For me, it’s the dream of being able to buy a home. Let’s work together to bring back the positive momentum for Dogecoin. We’re counting on you!”
